      <h3>Quick Answer</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Extended soreness (3+ days) after moderate exercise is usually a protein problem, not an age problem.</li>
        <li>Muscle repair requires amino acids from dietary protein — when intake is low, repair slows and inflammation lingers.</li>
